<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>Probably the most demanding project of my career in terms of complexity and client communication. Maximum expectations, very tight deadlines, international visibility and almost no margin for error. The luxury footwear world does not forgive mistakes, and this taught me that making decisions is not the hard part. Keeping them and building consistency out of them across everything that follows is. There is no going back. Every decision is live within a day.</p>
    <p>This was also a significant moment for something else: proving that remote work has no real limitations when done properly. The collaboration started during lockdown and lasted several years. There were calls at 3 or 4 in the morning with stakeholders on other continents, entire months without seeing colleagues in person. The fair always went well. Every brief was met. Every problem, technical or human, was resolved.</p>
